https://slackbuilds.org/repository/15.0/development/qt-creator-llvm/?search=qt-creator-llvm
This package provides LLVM/Clang components required by Qt Creator
in order to extend Qt Creator's functionality. You need to install
this package prior to compiling Qt Creator to make it work.

Some of the Qt Creator's tools enabled by this package are:
- Clang Code Model,
- Clang-Tidy,
- Clazy,
- Clang Static Analyzer.
